00:53:16,994 --> 00:53:20,454
And then Hans goes,
“] must do that music."

815
00:53:20,998 --> 00:53:24,688
And he really nailed
that genre of bachelor pad.

816
00:53:29,573 --> 00:53:31,413
Here come our spit takes.

