00:53:31,742 --> 00:53:34,732
So this is one where we had a few
and thought they were funny.

818
00:53:36,447 --> 00:53:38,467
The problem was
we didn't have enough,

819
00:53:38,816 --> 00:53:40,926
so we added more.

820
00:53:59,903 --> 00:54:02,272
In the issue of food,
they're so pampered in a zoo,

821
00:54:02,673 --> 00:54:04,252
we're like, well how can we...?

822
00:54:05,709 --> 00:54:08,749
They wouldn't know what to look for
to find food, you know.

823
00:54:09,246 --> 00:54:11,496
They didn't even know
food grows on trees.

824
00:54:11,882 --> 00:54:14,052
So they're kind of helpless
in this environment

825
00:54:14,418 --> 00:54:15,728
being naive about the wild.

826
00:54:15,986 --> 00:54:19,386
And this is a good way to show
the herbivores

827
00:54:19,923 --> 00:54:22,352
are OK with this stuff,

828
00:54:22,760 --> 00:54:25,660
but Alex needs his steak.

829
00:54:26,130 --> 00:54:27,860
So it was a moment we could put in

830
00:54:28,165 --> 00:54:31,005
where Alex really starts
to get hungry here.

831
00:54:50,687 --> 00:54:54,497
And Alex is hungry for steak.
It was always thought...

832
00:54:55,092 --> 00:54:57,642
It was always a moment
for him to have this dream.

833
00:54:58,061 --> 00:55:00,721
We tried different versions
of these different dreams.

834
00:55:01,165 --> 00:55:04,705
One was based off Jurassic Park
where there are steaks running around

835
00:55:05,269 --> 00:55:08,578
in flocks and herds
on a big savannah. And then...

836
00:55:09,106 --> 00:55:12,036
We had a big dance number,

837
00:55:12,509 --> 00:55:14,349
with all the steaks sort of...

838
00:55:14,678 --> 00:55:17,018
Another Busby Berkeley musical,

839
00:55:17,414 --> 00:55:20,224
and again,
the story artists had come up

840
00:55:20,684 --> 00:55:24,314
with this idea,
based off the movie.

