00:55:24,888 --> 00:55:28,078
But it was just a real simple
quick way we could convey

842
00:55:28,592 --> 00:55:32,752
and have a little joke about it,
that Alex loves steak.

843
00:55:33,397 --> 00:55:36,417
Rob Koo, one of our board artists,
added him doing a steak angel,

844
00:55:36,900 --> 00:55:38,450
which he then added to that.

845
00:55:41,805 --> 00:55:45,085
We actually added these cutbacks
so that we could extend this moment,

846
00:55:45,609 --> 00:55:47,069
make it very uncomfortable.

847
00:55:54,017 --> 00:55:57,006
It sort of cracks me up
that Marty kind of buys it.

848
00:55:57,487 --> 00:55:58,537
Yeah.

849
00:55:58,755 --> 00:56:01,155
Hey, what do you know?

850
00:56:15,372 --> 00:56:18,361
Just the cadence of Sacha's voice
make me laugh.

851
00:56:24,715 --> 00:56:26,705
Yeah, it's the Greek chorus up there

852
00:56:27,050 --> 00:56:29,390
commenting on Alex.

853
00:56:31,054 --> 00:56:32,634
The locals are desperate.

