00:56:32,923 --> 00:56:34,792
They need some kind of help.

855
00:56:36,526 --> 00:56:37,866
Just blabbing on.

856
00:56:39,396 --> 00:56:41,296
This was quite challenging
to do this.

857
00:56:41,632 --> 00:56:43,772
It's really funny on paper
when it's a drawing,

858
00:56:44,134 --> 00:56:48,114
all these lemurs pulling into this tree,
but to actually do it is very difficult.

859
00:56:52,209 --> 00:56:55,808
In traditional animation all you
need to do is draw it and paint it.

860
00:56:57,414 --> 00:57:01,394
In the computer world though
you have to build it.

861
00:57:02,019 --> 00:57:05,479
And on that gag and this one
coming up here,

862
00:57:06,023 --> 00:57:08,393
we adjusted the timings on those
over and over again

863
00:57:08,792 --> 00:57:11,752
trying to find the perfect rhythm.

