00:58:11,355 --> 00:58:14,105
They don't have to be where
Mother Nature tells them to be

879
00:58:14,558 --> 00:58:15,928
or New York or anything else.

880
00:58:16,193 --> 00:58:18,973
So the penguins again
are a parallel to that idea.

881
00:58:19,429 --> 00:58:22,909
Here Marty finds
the real version of his mural

882
00:58:23,467 --> 00:58:25,717
and thinks that that's all
he needs to be happy.

883
00:58:28,438 --> 00:58:30,898
But Alex is a good enough sport
to go along

884
00:58:31,308 --> 00:58:33,328
after their reconciliation
on the beach.

885
00:58:37,180 --> 00:58:39,460
