00:58:39,850 --> 00:58:44,009
How do we get... We wanted Marty
to bring this kind of wild side out.

887
00:58:47,391 --> 00:58:51,311
We thought if we could get him
into that chase kind of situation,

888
00:58:51,928 --> 00:58:54,857
a game of tag, that Alex's instincts
would somehow kick in,

889
00:58:55,332 --> 00:58:58,372
between the hunger and
just the act of chasing his friend.

890
00:59:00,604 --> 00:59:02,823
We didn't necessarily have
that dream sequence

891
00:59:03,206 --> 00:59:04,576
at the beginning of the film

