00:59:27,164 --> 00:59:29,334
There's a similar shot
to Marty's fantasy.

897
00:59:32,903 --> 00:59:35,743
So now Alex's pupils
have changed.

898
00:59:37,441 --> 00:59:41,310
He's transitioned into something
closer to a wild cat,

899
00:59:41,912 --> 00:59:45,662
something's flowing inside of him
that he's never felt before.

900
00:59:49,119 --> 00:59:51,459
We wanted to have something
for Alex that would show

901
00:59:51,855 --> 00:59:54,135
like when he's a little bit crazed
and more wild,

