00:59:58,128 --> 01:00:00,348
And then there's three wigs also
to kind of show

904
01:00:00,730 --> 01:00:03,360
how he would progress
and get a little wilder.

905
01:00:03,800 --> 01:00:05,550
Here's the next version of his hair,

906
01:00:05,869 --> 01:00:09,089
which isn't quite as
blow-dried as normal.

907
01:00:10,774 --> 01:00:14,314
And his whiskers start to get
little kinks in them as well.

908
01:00:16,546 --> 01:00:18,245
Look how he just throws this lemur.

909
01:00:23,820 --> 01:00:24,990
Animators having fun.

910
01:00:27,224 --> 01:00:30,624
This is a great example of Sacha
coming up with alternate wording.

911
01:00:35,699 --> 01:00:37,099
"In a very good working..."

912
01:00:37,367 --> 01:00:39,947
It was something like,
"My plan is working excellently,"

913
01:00:40,370 --> 01:00:44,000
in the script, and he turned it
into words that Julien would say.

914
01:00:57,387 --> 01:01:01,167
We used to have this long scene
where Alex was sniffing Marty,

915
01:01:01,758 --> 01:01:05,038
with that wild look on his face
and didn't know what smelled so good.

916
01:01:05,562 --> 01:01:09,042
Thought he smelled steak and he...
