917
01:01:18,275 --> 01:01:20,385
Sort of a variation on the song
that we heard

918
01:01:20,744 --> 01:01:22,964
when Alex was at the zoo,

919
01:01:23,346 --> 01:01:26,976
with kind of a crazy,
marching band feel to it.

920
01:01:30,587 --> 01:01:33,167
And once Julien's character
was, you know,

921
01:01:33,590 --> 01:01:36,460
challenged by another king,

