01:01:36,927 --> 01:01:39,147
he became kind of bitter about Alex.

923
01:01:39,529 --> 01:01:41,309
And there was a lot more of that,

924
01:01:41,631 --> 01:01:44,321
but then we kind of pulled back
on that, because...

925
01:01:45,368 --> 01:01:47,998
A beautiful waterfall back there
through these scenes

926
01:01:48,438 --> 01:01:50,278
that we had turned off earlier.

927
01:01:55,045 --> 01:01:59,205
So it was how to show Alex
going nuts, and his point of view.

928
01:01:59,849 --> 01:02:02,919
And, you know,
gotta give credit to older cartoons

929
01:02:03,420 --> 01:02:06,350
that would turn someone
into a sucker,

930
01:02:06,823 --> 01:02:09,283
you know,
and cross-dissolve.

