01:03:01,778 --> 01:03:04,678
It was Maurice like a car salesman,

947
01:03:05,148 --> 01:03:06,928
showing all the attributes of a lion.

948
01:03:07,250 --> 01:03:11,590
The teeth, the claws,
built for speed, four-wheel drive.

