So this is something
at the end of production,

1171
01:19:20,222 --> 01:19:24,201
they're sundries animation,
but a lot of it was just...

1172
01:19:24,827 --> 01:19:28,047
A lot of animators
had some time and said,

1173
01:19:28,564 --> 01:19:31,584
"What's your favorite character?
